UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='How goes the search and recovery mission, $n?  We really need to get those Logs and Charts back from the Maiden\'s Folly and Spirit of Silverpine.$B$BIf the information from those sources were to fall into enemy hands, Fleet Master Seahorn would force us down the plank.$B$BThat is if we ever get out of this mess...' WHERE entry=662; -- RequestItemsText: How goes the search and recovery mission, $n?  We really need to get those Logs and Charts back from the Maiden\'s Folly and Spirit of Silverpine.$B$BIf the information from those sources were to fall into enemy hands, Fleet Master Seahorn would force us down the plank.$B$BThat is if we ever get out of this mess...
UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='Bah, maybe I should go kill those naga scum myself. It\'s obvious you\'re not goin\' to do it.$B$BMaybe I can find some knitting needles so you can keep yourself busy.' WHERE entry=664; -- RequestItemsText: Bah, maybe I should go kill those naga scum myself. It\'s obvious you\'re not goin\' to do it.$B$BMaybe I can find some knitting needles so you can keep yourself busy.
