UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='Perhaps I was not explicit in my orders, $c. I want High Inquisitor Whitemane killed once and for all. And while you\'re at it, take out her top brass as well.$B$BKill that zealot, Scarlet Commander Mograine. Lay waste to Herod, the Scarlet Champion. And slaughter Houndmaster Loksey and his filthy mutts too.$B$BNow begone!' WHERE entry=1048; -- RequestItemsText: Perhaps I was not explicit in my orders, $c. I want High Inquisitor Whitemane killed once and for all. And while you\'re at it, take out her top brass as well.$B$BKill that zealot, Scarlet Commander Mograine. Lay waste to Herod, the Scarlet Champion. And slaughter Houndmaster Loksey and his filthy mutts too.$B$BNow begone!
UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='Cairne is a brave and noble leader and I would trust him with my own life. But it is others that I do not trust in this political climate.$B$BOnce I have a chance to gather all the knowledge available I can provide sound council to the Chieftain.$B$BHave you had a chance to travel to Tirisfal Glades? To the Scarlet Monastery? The Compendium of the Fallen is just one piece in this complicated puzzle...' WHERE entry=1049; -- RequestItemsText: Cairne is a brave and noble leader and I would trust him with my own life. But it is others that I do not trust in this political climate.$B$BOnce I have a chance to gather all the knowledge available I can provide sound council to the Chieftain.$B$BHave you had a chance to travel to Tirisfal Glades? To the Scarlet Monastery? The Compendium of the Fallen is just one piece in this complicated puzzle...
UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='The Monastery was a seminary for Paladins-in-training. Once a stronghold of the Light, it fell into the hands of the crazed zealots of the Scarlet Crusade.$B$BThe Crusade believed their goal a noble one: to purify the land of the undead plague. But insanity tainted their plight and now they stand enemies to all.$B$BBring Mythology of the Titans to me so I can study it and house it here in Ironforge.$B$BThe corrupt halls of the Monastery are no place for such a historical treasure.' WHERE entry=1050; -- RequestItemsText: The Monastery was a seminary for Paladins-in-training. Once a stronghold of the Light, it fell into the hands of the crazed zealots of the Scarlet Crusade.$B$BThe Crusade believed their goal a noble one: to purify the land of the undead plague. But insanity tainted their plight and now they stand enemies to all.$B$BBring Mythology of the Titans to me so I can study it and house it here in Ironforge.$B$BThe corrupt halls of the Monastery are no place for such a historical treasure.
