UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc2='', offerrewardtext_loc2='Here\'s your armor, $N. This will stand up to the strongest assaults or my name isn\'t Furen Longbeard!$B$BAnd I have to thank you. I learned a lot while working with the materials$Byou brought me. I think I\'ll have another breakthrough one day!$B$BI\'m going to send what I learned to other$Bblacksmiths of the Alliance.$B$BI\'ll tell them you were a big help, and maybe they\'ll want to return the favor.' WHERE entry=1782; -- offerrewardtext: Here\'s your armor, $N. This will stand up to the strongest assaults or my name isn\'t Furen Longbeard!$B$BAnd I have to thank you. I learned a lot while working with the materials$Byou brought me. I think I\'ll have another breakthrough one day!$B$BI\'m going to send what I learned to other$Bblacksmiths of the Alliance.$B$BI\'ll tell them you were a big help, and maybe they\'ll want to return the favor.
