UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='Yes, may I help you with something?  I assure you I am a very busy right now.  If it is grave importance to the Explorers\' League, however, then I am all ears!' WHERE entry=2279; -- RequestItemsText: Yes, may I help you with something?  I assure you I am a very busy right now.  If it is grave importance to the Explorers\' League, however, then I am all ears!
UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='Yes young one, I see you marching into my tent with intensity in your stride... with determination in your purpose. You seek my counsel is some matter of grave importance to the Horde? Perhaps you wish a mystery of the universe revealed to you?' WHERE entry=2280; -- RequestItemsText: Yes young one, I see you marching into my tent with intensity in your stride... with determination in your purpose. You seek my counsel is some matter of grave importance to the Horde? Perhaps you wish a mystery of the universe revealed to you?
