UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='I\'ve been watching Lescovar for a couple weeks now. Trias has never trusted him, but we didn\'t suspect he was involved in anything to do with the Defias Brotherhood. We were following leads that tied him to the Twilight\'s Hammer. Either way, he\'s become more dangerous than this city can deal with, and that\'s where we come in.$B$BGet me those items and we can put my plan into effect.' WHERE entry=2746; -- RequestItemsText: I\'ve been watching Lescovar for a couple weeks now. Trias has never trusted him, but we didn\'t suspect he was involved in anything to do with the Defias Brotherhood. We were following leads that tied him to the Twilight\'s Hammer. Either way, he\'s become more dangerous than this city can deal with, and that\'s where we come in.$B$BGet me those items and we can put my plan into effect.
