UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='Elune\'adore, $C.  What may I do for you today?' WHERE entry=4510; -- RequestItemsText: Elune\'adore, $C.  What may I do for you today?
UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='Zug zug!  What may I help you with today, $C?' WHERE entry=4511; -- RequestItemsText: Zug zug!  What may I help you with today, $C?
UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='Some of the experiments I\'ve done are fascinating. I think with a little more work, I\'ll be able to figure out the nature of these creatures and how they play into how life developed on Azeroth... if they even have anything to do with it to begin with.$B$BOne of my biggest theories that isn\'t well liked is the idea that oozes and slimes are tied to the creation of this planet... almost like they\'re a secretion of it.$B$BBut I can\'t prove or disprove it until I get more samples.' WHERE entry=4512; -- RequestItemsText: Some of the experiments I\'ve done are fascinating. I think with a little more work, I\'ll be able to figure out the nature of these creatures and how they play into how life developed on Azeroth... if they even have anything to do with it to begin with.$B$BOne of my biggest theories that isn\'t well liked is the idea that oozes and slimes are tied to the creation of this planet... almost like they\'re a secretion of it.$B$BBut I can\'t prove or disprove it until I get more samples.
UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='So many things to consider. But what does it mean? And how does it affect the lives of the people of Azeroth?' WHERE entry=4513; -- RequestItemsText: So many things to consider. But what does it mean? And how does it affect the lives of the people of Azeroth?
