UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc2='', offerrewardtext_loc2='You pick up the petri dish with the slime sample in it. The only way to discern if the samples is pure enough is to open it and examine the contents yourself. Ideally you\'ll find a sample that fits Chemist Fuely\'s criteria.' WHERE entry=4561; -- offerrewardtext: You pick up the petri dish with the slime sample in it. The only way to discern if the samples is pure enough is to open it and examine the contents yourself. Ideally you\'ll find a sample that fits Chemist Fuely\'s criteria.
UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='You take a sample of slime from Un\'Goro Crater and place some of it into the various tubes and beakers on the table. As things begin to boil and spurt, the slime changes colors. When the process slows down and the liquids calm, you see a small petri dish with your purified Un\'Goro slime samples in it along with some other remnants.' WHERE entry=4561; -- RequestItemsText: You take a sample of slime from Un\'Goro Crater and place some of it into the various tubes and beakers on the table. As things begin to boil and spurt, the slime changes colors. When the process slows down and the liquids calm, you see a small petri dish with your purified Un\'Goro slime samples in it along with some other remnants.
UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='Do you have something for me?' WHERE entry=4581; -- RequestItemsText: Do you have something for me?
UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='It would seem that the device needs some sort of grime-encrusted object to clean and three silver coins to get the contraption working. So long as both are present, the Sparklematic 5200 should work...' WHERE entry=4601; -- RequestItemsText: It would seem that the device needs some sort of grime-encrusted object to clean and three silver coins to get the contraption working. So long as both are present, the Sparklematic 5200 should work...
