UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='We know that each cauldron employs a different mix of reagents to generate its plague-inducing toxin; likewise, we know that we will need to develop a counter agent that is unique for each cauldron. Your sample from Dalson\'s Tears will be the key to figure out that cauldron\'s distinct reagent requirement.' WHERE entry=5220; -- RequestItemsText: We know that each cauldron employs a different mix of reagents to generate its plague-inducing toxin; likewise, we know that we will need to develop a counter agent that is unique for each cauldron. Your sample from Dalson\'s Tears will be the key to figure out that cauldron\'s distinct reagent requirement.
