UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc2='', offerrewardtext_loc2='Congratulations, $N - I am pleased to award you with an Argent Dawn valor token!$B$BThe tokens serve two purposes. One - they can be used to further your standing within the Argent Dawn; to do so may avail you options and rewards that are reserved for our honored and revered allies. Two - they can be given to our quartermasters, along with coin, as payment for some of the Dawn\'s more prized items.$B$BWhatever you decide, know that you are earning your commission. Well done!' WHERE entry=5408; -- offerrewardtext: Congratulations, $N - I am pleased to award you with an Argent Dawn valor token!$B$BThe tokens serve two purposes. One - they can be used to further your standing within the Argent Dawn; to do so may avail you options and rewards that are reserved for our honored and revered allies. Two - they can be given to our quartermasters, along with coin, as payment for some of the Dawn\'s more prized items.$B$BWhatever you decide, know that you are earning your commission. Well done!
