UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='Salutations, mighty priest! Have you brought the valor tokens I asked of you? Once you hand them to me, I will issue you your own Chromatic Mantle of the Dawn.' WHERE entry=5517; -- RequestItemsText: Salutations, mighty priest! Have you brought the valor tokens I asked of you? Once you hand them to me, I will issue you your own Chromatic Mantle of the Dawn.
UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='The Ogre Tannin is probably the toughest thing to find for what I need to make the suit - I think they have some upstairs?  It\'s hard to tell, since this ball and chain doesn\'t make movement that easy to do...$B$BAnyway, bring me the things I need, and I\'ll whip you up an ogre suit that will fool Captain Kromcrush into thinking you\'re one of his men.' WHERE entry=5518; -- RequestItemsText: The Ogre Tannin is probably the toughest thing to find for what I need to make the suit - I think they have some upstairs?  It\'s hard to tell, since this ball and chain doesn\'t make movement that easy to do...$B$BAnyway, bring me the things I need, and I\'ll whip you up an ogre suit that will fool Captain Kromcrush into thinking you\'re one of his men.
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc2='', offerrewardtext_loc2='Here ya go $N - put this thing on, and you\'ll have ten minutes to do whatever.  Good luck!$B$BOh, and if you happen to find a key to get me out of here, BY ALL MEANS LET ME KNOW!!!' WHERE entry=5519; -- offerrewardtext: Here ya go $N - put this thing on, and you\'ll have ten minutes to do whatever.  Good luck!$B$BOh, and if you happen to find a key to get me out of here, BY ALL MEANS LET ME KNOW!!!
