UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='You have something to tell me, $C?' WHERE entry=8502; -- RequestItemsText: You have something to tell me, $C?
UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='It\'s not true! I\'d never skim any stranglekelp off the top of the stacks here. One might be tempted to though considering that it\'s practically a panacea of utilitarian usefulness. *cough* You don\'t happen to have that stranglekelp we discussed earlier?' WHERE entry=8503; -- RequestItemsText: It\'s not true! I\'d never skim any stranglekelp off the top of the stacks here. One might be tempted to though considering that it\'s practically a panacea of utilitarian usefulness. *cough* You don\'t happen to have that stranglekelp we discussed earlier?
UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='Do you have the purple lotus herbs that I requested?' WHERE entry=8505; -- RequestItemsText: Do you have the purple lotus herbs that I requested?
UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='You\'ll find Captain Blackanvil\'s force stationed outside Hive\'Zora.  Talk to his lieutenant, Janela Stouthammer, if you can\'t find him.' WHERE entry=8507; -- RequestItemsText: You\'ll find Captain Blackanvil\'s force stationed outside Hive\'Zora.  Talk to his lieutenant, Janela Stouthammer, if you can\'t find him.
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc2='', offerrewardtext_loc2='Aye, I suppose that little skirmish will pass as field duty nowadays. Take these back to Cenarion Hold, I\'m sure they\'ll have a cushy job ready for you.$B$BOff you go!' WHERE entry=8508; -- offerrewardtext: Aye, I suppose that little skirmish will pass as field duty nowadays. Take these back to Cenarion Hold, I\'m sure they\'ll have a cushy job ready for you.$B$BOff you go!
UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='I take it you want those papers signed, $Glad:lass;?' WHERE entry=8508; -- RequestItemsText: I take it you want those papers signed, $Glad:lass;?
UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='What\'s that? Speak up, $C! Have you got that shipment of Arthas\' Tears I asked for?' WHERE entry=8509; -- RequestItemsText: What\'s that? Speak up, $C! Have you got that shipment of Arthas\' Tears I asked for?
UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='$C, I do so hope that\'s the light leather you promised.' WHERE entry=8511; -- RequestItemsText: $C, I do so hope that\'s the light leather you promised.
UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='Good to see you again, $N. It does appear that we need more light leather for the creation of the various war materiels. If you would bring me a stack of ten, that would be just perfect.' WHERE entry=8512; -- RequestItemsText: Good to see you again, $N. It does appear that we need more light leather for the creation of the various war materiels. If you would bring me a stack of ten, that would be just perfect.
UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='Yes sir, I remember you. Is that the medium leather you have with you there?' WHERE entry=8513; -- RequestItemsText: Yes sir, I remember you. Is that the medium leather you have with you there?
UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='Yes sir, looks like we\'ve collected many pieces of medium leather, but we need more. I can assure you that it will all be put to good use; not one piece will get wasted. I know it\'s a lot to ask, but if you\'re still willing, I could use your help in attempting to put a dent in the rest of my quota.' WHERE entry=8514; -- RequestItemsText: Yes sir, looks like we\'ve collected many pieces of medium leather, but we need more. I can assure you that it will all be put to good use; not one piece will get wasted. I know it\'s a lot to ask, but if you\'re still willing, I could use your help in attempting to put a dent in the rest of my quota.
UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='Is that the thick leather you have there in your pack, $C? Is it? I can\'t wait for you to hand it over! Everyone is going to be so pleased with us don\'t you think?' WHERE entry=8515; -- RequestItemsText: Is that the thick leather you have there in your pack, $C? Is it? I can\'t wait for you to hand it over! Everyone is going to be so pleased with us don\'t you think?
UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='Yep, the stack\'s still not high enough. $N, we still haven\'t reached our thick leather goal. Just think of all the things that we can make with all of that leather! All kinds of armor and weapons. Stuff for inside the steam tanks and rifle scopes! And engineering goggles, those are always fun!$B$BYou gonna bring me back some more thick leather?' WHERE entry=8516; -- RequestItemsText: Yep, the stack\'s still not high enough. $N, we still haven\'t reached our thick leather goal. Just think of all the things that we can make with all of that leather! All kinds of armor and weapons. Stuff for inside the steam tanks and rifle scopes! And engineering goggles, those are always fun!$B$BYou gonna bring me back some more thick leather?
UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='Do you have the twenty linen bandages that I require, $C?' WHERE entry=8517; -- RequestItemsText: Do you have the twenty linen bandages that I require, $C?
