UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='I need those tunics and headbands made, and I also need that piece of wildvine before I will share with you the knowledge of Wild Leather helmets.$B$BHead gear is highly coveted amongst adventurers, whether it be a disarmingly simple headband or a full-covering helmet. The fundamentals of creating valued head gear remain constant, no matter what the cosmetic appearance of the gear is.' WHERE entry=8520; -- RequestItemsText: I need those tunics and headbands made, and I also need that piece of wildvine before I will share with you the knowledge of Wild Leather helmets.$B$BHead gear is highly coveted amongst adventurers, whether it be a disarmingly simple headband or a full-covering helmet. The fundamentals of creating valued head gear remain constant, no matter what the cosmetic appearance of the gear is.
UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='It is very kind of you to offer to help me again, $c. It looks like we\'ve collected a goodly number of the silk bandages we\'ve been tasked with, but we still need more. $N, is there any way that you could see fit to put together another bundle and return them to me here? The Alliance and I will be most grateful.' WHERE entry=8521; -- RequestItemsText: It is very kind of you to offer to help me again, $c. It looks like we\'ve collected a goodly number of the silk bandages we\'ve been tasked with, but we still need more. $N, is there any way that you could see fit to put together another bundle and return them to me here? The Alliance and I will be most grateful.
UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='The days pass one after the other, and still we go on. $C, have you those runecloth bandages?' WHERE entry=8522; -- RequestItemsText: The days pass one after the other, and still we go on. $C, have you those runecloth bandages?
UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='So it is that we come to discuss pressing matters yet again, $C. Once more I thank you for your previous efforts; it is not everyone who would give so selflessly. But there is still more work to do.$B$B$N, will you once more collect runecloth bandages and return them to me here?' WHERE entry=8523; -- RequestItemsText: So it is that we come to discuss pressing matters yet again, $C. Once more I thank you for your previous efforts; it is not everyone who would give so selflessly. But there is still more work to do.$B$B$N, will you once more collect runecloth bandages and return them to me here?
UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='I\'m willing to lay odds that you\'ve returned with all of that rainbow fin albacore we were talking about before, right, $C?' WHERE entry=8524; -- RequestItemsText: I\'m willing to lay odds that you\'ve returned with all of that rainbow fin albacore we were talking about before, right, $C?
UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='What! You again? Well I\'ll be a monkey\'s uncle... except that I\'m a gnome. Slicky Gastronome to be precise! So you\'re back to help out again, eh? Well, I can\'t say as I blame you. Don\'t you just love the smell of all of that food? <drool>$B$BEnough loitering! Get out there and bring me back more rainbow fin albacore!' WHERE entry=8525; -- RequestItemsText: What! You again? Well I\'ll be a monkey\'s uncle... except that I\'m a gnome. Slicky Gastronome to be precise! So you\'re back to help out again, eh? Well, I can\'t say as I blame you. Don\'t you just love the smell of all of that food? <drool>$B$BEnough loitering! Get out there and bring me back more rainbow fin albacore!
UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='So do you have all of that roast raptor yet?' WHERE entry=8526; -- RequestItemsText: So do you have all of that roast raptor yet?
UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='I am confident that you are returning so soon with the spotted yellowtail we discussed.' WHERE entry=8528; -- RequestItemsText: I am confident that you are returning so soon with the spotted yellowtail we discussed.
