UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='Back so soon? You\'ll be a real miner in no time, $C. So, you already know the drill; I need you to go out, mine up a mess of copper ore, smelt it into bars and bring it back to me here. I know that\'s something you\'re capable of, the question is, are you willing?' WHERE entry=8533; -- RequestItemsText: Back so soon? You\'ll be a real miner in no time, $C. So, you already know the drill; I need you to go out, mine up a mess of copper ore, smelt it into bars and bring it back to me here. I know that\'s something you\'re capable of, the question is, are you willing?
